name: Vinny and the Factory with Cash
name_original: Vinny and the Factory with Cash
description:
Vinny needs cash to buy the latest video game. Help him navigate the abandoned factory and use the batteries to power and navigate the various obstacles.

Instructions:

  • Move with Arrow Keys or WASD
  • Enter doors with Up or W
  • Jump with Space

Made for Ready Set Jam

  • Hosted by VimLark
  • In competition with Helper Wesley
  • Theme: Power Sources and Restriction: Achievements
